# Visitor Management UI

Before designing or changing UI, read and follow `/DESIGN.md`.

## Design system (required)

- Primary: Red `#E11D48`
- Secondary: Pink `#F472B6`
- Surfaces: White / Light Gray `#F4F4F5`
- Text: Dark Navy `#0F172A`
- Font: Poppins
- Cards: large radius (16–20px), minimal shadow
- Feel: Linear / Notion / Stripe / Framer dashboards

Use CSS tokens in `frontend/src/styles/tokens.css`. Do not introduce a green or purple brand theme.

## Product surfaces

1. Mobile PWA (primary) — home, approvals, gate, pass, profile
2. Public pass page — `/vms/pass/<visitor-entry>`
3. Desk Form — Visitor Entry workflow (Pending → Check-in → Approved → Meeting Done → Check Out)

After frontend changes: `cd frontend && npm run build`.
